<search>
  <entry>
    <title>Hexo + GitHub Pages 完整指南：从安装到美化</title>
    <url>/2026/03/18/hexo-github-pages-guide/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<blockquote>
<p>想要拥有一个属于自己的技术博客？本教程将手把手教你使用 Hexo 和 GitHub Pages 免费搭建一个漂亮且功能完善的个人博客。</p>
</blockquote>
<span id="more"></span>

<h2 id="目录"><a href="#目录" class="headerlink" title="目录"></a>目录</h2><ol>
<li><a href="#%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%87%86%E5%A4%87">环境准备</a></li>
<li><a href="#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85-hexo">安装 Hexo</a></li>
<li><a href="#%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA%E5%92%8C%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2">创建和配置博客</a></li>
<li><a href="#%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E5%88%B0-github-pages">部署到 GitHub Pages</a></li>
<li><a href="#%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96">主题美化</a></li>
<li><a href="#%E8%BF%9B%E9%98%B6%E6%8A%80%E5%B7%A7">进阶技巧</a></li>
</ol>
<hr>
<h2 id="环境准备"><a href="#环境准备" class="headerlink" title="环境准备"></a>环境准备</h2><p>在开始之前，请确保你的电脑已安装以下工具：</p>
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th>工具</th>
<th>版本要求</th>
<th>下载地址</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody><tr>
<td>Node.js</td>
<td>&gt;&#x3D; 14.0</td>
<td><a href="https://nodejs.org/">nodejs.org</a></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Git</td>
<td>任意版本</td>
<td><a href="https://git-scm.com/">git-scm.com</a></td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
<h3 id="验证安装"><a href="#验证安装" class="headerlink" title="验证安装"></a>验证安装</h3><p>打开终端，运行以下命令检查是否安装成功：</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 检查 Node.js 版本</span></span><br><span class="line">node -v</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 检查 npm 版本</span></span><br><span class="line">npm -v</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 检查 Git 版本</span></span><br><span class="line">git --version</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>如果都能正常显示版本号，说明环境准备就绪！</p>
<hr>
<h2 id="安装-Hexo"><a href="#安装-Hexo" class="headerlink" title="安装 Hexo"></a>安装 Hexo</h2><p>Hexo 是一个快速、简洁且高效的静态博客框架。使用 npm 即可轻松安装：</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 全局安装 Hexo CLI</span></span><br><span class="line">npm install -g hexo-cli</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 验证安装</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo -v</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>安装成功后，你会看到 Hexo 的版本信息。</p>
<hr>
<h2 id="创建和配置博客"><a href="#创建和配置博客" class="headerlink" title="创建和配置博客"></a>创建和配置博客</h2><h3 id="1-初始化博客项目"><a href="#1-初始化博客项目" class="headerlink" title="1. 初始化博客项目"></a>1. 初始化博客项目</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 创建博客目录（将 blog 替换为你想要的名称）</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo init blog</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> blog</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 安装依赖</span></span><br><span class="line">npm install</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>初始化完成后，目录结构如下：</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">blog/</span><br><span class="line">├── _config.yml          # 站点配置文件</span><br><span class="line">├── package.json         # 依赖包信息</span><br><span class="line">├── scaffolds/           # 模板文件夹</span><br><span class="line">├── source/              # 源码文件夹</span><br><span class="line">│   └── _posts/          # 博文存放目录</span><br><span class="line">└── themes/              # 主题文件夹</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="2-基础配置"><a href="#2-基础配置" class="headerlink" title="2. 基础配置"></a>2. 基础配置</h3><p>编辑 <code>_config.yml</code> 文件，配置你的博客信息：</p>
<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 站点信息</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">title:</span> <span class="string">我的博客</span>           <span class="comment"># 博客标题</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">subtitle:</span> <span class="string">&#x27;记录生活与技术&#x27;</span> <span class="comment"># 副标题</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">description:</span> <span class="string">&#x27;一个分享技术与生活的个人博客&#x27;</span>  <span class="comment"># 描述</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">keywords:</span> <span class="string">技术,</span> <span class="string">博客,</span> <span class="string">生活</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">author:</span> <span class="string">你的名字</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">language:</span> <span class="string">zh-CN</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">timezone:</span> <span class="string">&#x27;Asia/Shanghai&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># URL 配置</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">url:</span> <span class="string">https://你的用户名.github.io</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">permalink:</span> <span class="string">:year/:month/:day/:title/</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 部署配置</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">deploy:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">type:</span> <span class="string">git</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">repo:</span> <span class="string">git@github.com:你的GitHub用户名/你的用户名.github.io.git</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">branch:</span> <span class="string">main</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>由于GitHub 从 2021年8月起，彻底禁止使用账号密码进行 Git 命令行操作（包括 git push&#x2F;Hexo 部署），必须使用 Personal Access Token (PAT) 或 SSH 密钥 完成认证，因此deploy中的repo必须使用ssh地址。</p>
<h3 id="3-本地预览"><a href="#3-本地预览" class="headerlink" title="3. 本地预览"></a>3. 本地预览</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 生成静态文件</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo generate</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 或简写</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo g</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 启动本地服务器</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo server</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 或简写</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>访问 <code>http://localhost:4000</code> 即可预览你的博客。</p>
<h3 id="4-创建第一篇博文"><a href="#4-创建第一篇博文" class="headerlink" title="4. 创建第一篇博文"></a>4. 创建第一篇博文</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 创建新文章</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo new post <span class="string">&quot;我的第一篇博文&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>这会在 <code>source/_posts/</code> 目录下生成一个 Markdown 文件，编辑它：</p>
<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: 我的第一篇博文</span><br><span class="line">date: 2026-03-18 19:00:00</span><br><span class="line">tags:</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">  -</span> 随笔</span><br><span class="line">categories:</span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">  - 生活</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">---</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section"># 我的第一篇博文</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">欢迎来到我的博客！这是我的第一篇文章。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<hr>
<h2 id="部署到-GitHub-Pages"><a href="#部署到-GitHub-Pages" class="headerlink" title="部署到 GitHub Pages"></a>部署到 GitHub Pages</h2><h3 id="1-创建-GitHub-仓库"><a href="#1-创建-GitHub-仓库" class="headerlink" title="1. 创建 GitHub 仓库"></a>1. 创建 GitHub 仓库</h3><ol>
<li>登录 GitHub，点击右上角 <strong>+</strong> 号 → <strong>New repository</strong></li>
<li>仓库名填写：<code>你的用户名.github.io</code>（例如：<code>zhangsan.github.io</code>）</li>
<li>选择 <strong>Public</strong> 公开仓库</li>
<li>点击 <strong>Create repository</strong></li>
</ol>
<h3 id="2-安装部署插件"><a href="#2-安装部署插件" class="headerlink" title="2. 安装部署插件"></a>2. 安装部署插件</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="3-配置部署信息"><a href="#3-配置部署信息" class="headerlink" title="3. 配置部署信息"></a>3. 配置部署信息</h3><p>确保 <code>_config.yml</code> 中的 deploy 部分已正确配置（见上文）。</p>
<h3 id="4-执行部署"><a href="#4-执行部署" class="headerlink" title="4. 执行部署"></a>4. 执行部署</h3><p>首先检查ssh连接：</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ssh -T git@github.com </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>如果不正常，则需要先配置SSH连接：</p>
<h4 id="步骤-1：生成-SSH-密钥（本地）"><a href="#步骤-1：生成-SSH-密钥（本地）" class="headerlink" title="步骤 1：生成 SSH 密钥（本地）"></a>步骤 1：生成 SSH 密钥（本地）</h4><p>打开终端 &#x2F; 命令行，执行以下命令（替换为你的 GitHub 邮箱）：</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 生成 SSH 密钥（一路回车，无需设置密码）</span></span><br><span class="line">ssh-keygen -t ed25519 -C <span class="string">&quot;你的GitHub邮箱@example.com&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>执行后，密钥会生成在默认路径：<br>Windows：C:\Users\你的用户名.ssh\id_ed25519.pub<br>Mac&#x2F;Linux：~&#x2F;.ssh&#x2F;id_ed25519.pub</p>
<h4 id="步骤-2：将公钥添加到-GitHub"><a href="#步骤-2：将公钥添加到-GitHub" class="headerlink" title="步骤 2：将公钥添加到 GitHub"></a>步骤 2：将公钥添加到 GitHub</h4><h5 id="1-复制公钥内容："><a href="#1-复制公钥内容：" class="headerlink" title="1.复制公钥内容："></a>1.复制公钥内容：</h5><p>Windows：type C:\Users\你的用户名.ssh\id_ed25519.pub | clip<br>Mac&#x2F;Linux：cat ~&#x2F;.ssh&#x2F;id_ed25519.pub | pbcopy</p>
<h5 id="2-登录-GitHub-→-点击右上角头像-→-Settings-→-左侧-SSH-and-GPG-keys-→-New-SSH-key；"><a href="#2-登录-GitHub-→-点击右上角头像-→-Settings-→-左侧-SSH-and-GPG-keys-→-New-SSH-key；" class="headerlink" title="2.登录 GitHub → 点击右上角头像 → Settings → 左侧 SSH and GPG keys → New SSH key；"></a>2.登录 GitHub → 点击右上角头像 → Settings → 左侧 SSH and GPG keys → New SSH key；</h5><h5 id="3-Title-填任意名称（如「Hexo-博客部署」），Key-粘贴复制的公钥内容-→-点击-Add-SSH-key"><a href="#3-Title-填任意名称（如「Hexo-博客部署」），Key-粘贴复制的公钥内容-→-点击-Add-SSH-key" class="headerlink" title="3.Title 填任意名称（如「Hexo 博客部署」），Key 粘贴复制的公钥内容 → 点击 Add SSH key"></a>3.Title 填任意名称（如「Hexo 博客部署」），Key 粘贴复制的公钥内容 → 点击 Add SSH key</h5><p>再次验证SSH连接：</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 验证 SSH 连接（首次连接输入 yes 即可）</span></span><br><span class="line">ssh -T git@github.com</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 若输出「Hi 你的用户名! You&#x27;ve successfully authenticated...」则成功</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>SSH连接成功后再部署hexo</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 清理缓存（可选）</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo clean</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 生成并部署</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo deploy</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 或简写</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>首次部署会要求输入 GitHub 账号和密码（或使用 Token）。</p>
<h3 id="5-访问你的博客"><a href="#5-访问你的博客" class="headerlink" title="5. 访问你的博客"></a>5. 访问你的博客</h3><p>等待几分钟后，访问 <code>https://你的用户名.github.io</code> 即可看到你的博客！</p>
<hr>
<h2 id="主题美化"><a href="#主题美化" class="headerlink" title="主题美化"></a>主题美化</h2><p>Hexo 默认使用 landscape 主题，下面我们介绍如何更换和美化主题。</p>
<h3 id="1-更换主题"><a href="#1-更换主题" class="headerlink" title="1. 更换主题"></a>1. 更换主题</h3><p>Hexo 有丰富的主题生态，推荐几个热门主题：</p>
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th>主题名称</th>
<th>特点</th>
<th>GitHub 地址</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody><tr>
<td><strong>NexT</strong></td>
<td>功能丰富，文档完善</td>
<td><a href="https://github.com/next-theme/hexo-theme-next">next-theme&#x2F;hexo-theme-next</a></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>Butterfly</strong></td>
<td>美观精致，动画丰富</td>
<td><a href="https://github.com/jerryc127/hexo-theme-butterfly">jerryc127&#x2F;hexo-theme-butterfly</a></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>Fluid</strong></td>
<td>简约优雅，适合中文</td>
<td><a href="https://github.com/fluid-dev/hexo-theme-fluid">fluid-dev&#x2F;hexo-theme-fluid</a></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>Icarus</strong></td>
<td>卡片式设计</td>
<td><a href="https://github.com/ppoffice/hexo-theme-icarus">ppoffice&#x2F;hexo-theme-icarus</a></td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
<p>以 <strong>Butterfly</strong> 为例，演示主题安装：</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 进入博客目录</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> blog</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 克隆主题（使用最新版本）</span></span><br><span class="line">git <span class="built_in">clone</span> -b master https://github.com/jerryc127/hexo-theme-butterfly.git themes/butterfly</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 安装必要依赖</span></span><br><span class="line">npm install hexo-renderer-pug hexo-renderer-stylus --save</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>修改 <code>_config.yml</code>：</p>
<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">theme:</span> <span class="string">butterfly</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="2-主题基础配置（常用）"><a href="#2-主题基础配置（常用）" class="headerlink" title="2. 主题基础配置（常用）"></a>2. 主题基础配置（常用）</h3><p>复制 <code>themes/butterfly/_config.yml</code> 到博客根目录，并重命名为 <code>_config.butterfly.yml</code>，然后修改常用配置：</p>
<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 站点标题和副标题</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">title:</span> <span class="string">我的技术博客</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">subtitle:</span> <span class="string">专注技术分享与沉淀</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 头像</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">avatar:</span> <span class="string">/img/avatar.jpg</span>  <span class="comment"># 图片放在source/img目录下</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 导航栏</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">menu:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">首页:</span> <span class="string">/</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">归档:</span> <span class="string">/archives/</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">分类:</span> <span class="string">/categories/</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">标签:</span> <span class="string">/tags/</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">关于:</span> <span class="string">/about/</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 代码高亮</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">highlight_theme:</span> <span class="string">github</span>  <span class="comment"># 代码高亮风格</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="3-添加额外功能"><a href="#3-添加额外功能" class="headerlink" title="3. 添加额外功能"></a>3. 添加额外功能</h3><h4 id="3-1-添加搜索功能"><a href="#3-1-添加搜索功能" class="headerlink" title="3.1 添加搜索功能"></a>3.1 添加搜索功能</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-generator-searchdb --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>在 <code>_config.yml</code> 中添加：</p>
<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">search:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">path:</span> <span class="string">search.xml</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">field:</span> <span class="string">post</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">content:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">format:</span> <span class="string">html</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h4 id="3-2-添加字数统计"><a href="#3-2-添加字数统计" class="headerlink" title="3.2 添加字数统计"></a>3.2 添加字数统计</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-word-counter --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h4 id="3-3-添加-RSS-订阅"><a href="#3-3-添加-RSS-订阅" class="headerlink" title="3.3 添加 RSS 订阅"></a>3.3 添加 RSS 订阅</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-generator-feed --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>在 <code>_config.yml</code> 中添加：</p>
<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">feed:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">type:</span> <span class="string">atom</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">path:</span> <span class="string">atom.xml</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">limit:</span> <span class="number">20</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">content:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h4 id="3-4-添加网站图标"><a href="#3-4-添加网站图标" class="headerlink" title="3.4 添加网站图标"></a>3.4 添加网站图标</h4><p>准备 <code>favicon.ico</code> 文件，放入 <code>source/</code> 目录，然后在主题配置中设置：</p>
<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">favicon:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">small:</span> <span class="string">/favicon.ico</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">medium:</span> <span class="string">/favicon.ico</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">apple_touch_icon:</span> <span class="string">/favicon.ico</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="4-自定义样式"><a href="#4-自定义样式" class="headerlink" title="4. 自定义样式"></a>4. 自定义样式</h3><p>在主题目录的 <code>source/css/_custom/</code> 下创建 <code>custom.styl</code>：</p>
<figure class="highlight stylus"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 自定义字体</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">@font-face</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">font-family</span>: <span class="string">&#x27;CustomFont&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">src</span>: <span class="built_in">url</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;/fonts/custom.woff2&#x27;</span>) <span class="built_in">format</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;woff2&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="selector-tag">body</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">font-family</span>: <span class="string">&#x27;CustomFont&#x27;</span>, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 自定义链接颜色</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="selector-tag">a</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">color</span>: <span class="number">#1abc9c</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="selector-pseudo">&amp;:hover</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attribute">color</span>: <span class="number">#16a085</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 自定义代码块样式</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="selector-tag">code</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">background</span>: <span class="number">#f8f8f8</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">color</span>: <span class="number">#e74c3c</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 自定义文章宽度</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="selector-class">.main-inner</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">max-width</span>: <span class="number">900px</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<hr>
<h2 id="进阶技巧"><a href="#进阶技巧" class="headerlink" title="进阶技巧"></a>进阶技巧</h2><h3 id="1-常用-Hexo-命令"><a href="#1-常用-Hexo-命令" class="headerlink" title="1. 常用 Hexo 命令"></a>1. 常用 Hexo 命令</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 新建页面</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo new page <span class="string">&quot;关于&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 新建草稿</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo new draft <span class="string">&quot;草稿标题&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 发布草稿</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo publish draft <span class="string">&quot;草稿标题&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 清理缓存并重新生成</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo clean &amp;&amp; hexo generate</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 调试模式预览</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo server --debug</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 监听文件变化自动刷新</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo server --watch</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="2-图床方案"><a href="#2-图床方案" class="headerlink" title="2. 图床方案"></a>2. 图床方案</h3><p>推荐使用以下免费图床：</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>GitHub + jsDelivr</strong>：将图片上传到 GitHub 仓库，通过 jsDelivr CDN 加速访问</li>
<li><strong>SM.MS</strong>：免费图床服务</li>
<li><strong>Cloudinary</strong>：专业的图片托管服务</li>
</ul>
<p>Markdown 图片语法：</p>
<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">![<span class="string">图片描述</span>](<span class="link">https://你的图床地址/图片.png</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="3-多设备写作"><a href="#3-多设备写作" class="headerlink" title="3. 多设备写作"></a>3. 多设备写作</h3><p>将博客源码推送到 GitHub 另一个仓库（如 <code>blog-source</code>），在新设备上：</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git <span class="built_in">clone</span> https://github.com/你的用户名/blog-source.git</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> blog-source</span><br><span class="line">npm install</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="4-绑定自定义域名"><a href="#4-绑定自定义域名" class="headerlink" title="4. 绑定自定义域名"></a>4. 绑定自定义域名</h3><ol>
<li>在域名服务商处添加 CNAME 记录，指向 <code>你的用户名.github.io</code></li>
<li>在博客 <code>source/</code> 目录下创建 <code>CNAME</code> 文件，内容为你的域名：</li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">www.yourdomain.com</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<ol start="3">
<li>修改 <code>_config.yml</code>：</li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">url:</span> <span class="string">https://www.yourdomain.com</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<ol start="4">
<li>重新部署</li>
</ol>
<hr>
<h2 id="总结"><a href="#总结" class="headerlink" title="总结"></a>总结</h2><p>恭喜你！现在你已经拥有了一个：</p>
<p>✅ 免费的个人博客<br>✅ 使用 Hexo 静态生成<br>✅ 托管在 GitHub Pages<br>✅ 拥有精美主题和丰富功能</p>
<h3 id="下一步建议"><a href="#下一步建议" class="headerlink" title="下一步建议"></a>下一步建议</h3><ol>
<li>持续写作，积累优质内容</li>
<li>配置 Google Analytics 统计访问</li>
<li>添加 SEO 优化</li>
<li>接入评论系统（Giscus、Twikoo 等）</li>
<li>配置 CDN 加速</li>
</ol>
